function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 416') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.416!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (is_file('3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md') && (sha1_file('3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md') != '5def6975c0d6a07e614af3c3d2c708695544d9d5')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md');
	$tmp = pathinfo('3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}

	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md');
} else if (sha1_file('3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md') != '5def6975c0d6a07e614af3c3d2c708695544d9d5') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/bignumber.js/LICENCE.md');
}

if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') != 'f675bf2a9ba0a05b9da689d1f05b53556ac573d0') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/jstree/jstree.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') !== 'f675bf2a9ba0a05b9da689d1f05b53556ac573d0') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') !== 'c9b159160087e6dec4dd96be892ca53a436468eb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/jstree/jstree.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/jstree/jstree.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/jstree/jstree.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.js') !== 'f675bf2a9ba0a05b9da689d1f05b53556ac573d0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') != '7ee7168fd46455f0fd8bb237e6713eaa293e4b4c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') !== '7ee7168fd46455f0fd8bb237e6713eaa293e4b4c') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') !== 'f4c925236f6e0d578e4d4db8b6deb4a82cf90288') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/jstree.min.js') !== '7ee7168fd46455f0fd8bb237e6713eaa293e4b4c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/jstree.min.js');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png') != 'f4d101508f68f5efcf4cbf52199adf64756ebec5') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png') !== 'f4d101508f68f5efcf4cbf52199adf64756ebec5') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png') !== '0b8896011fa2f47e7cd9ae0f21025bf34ef064e3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png') !== 'f4d101508f68f5efcf4cbf52199adf64756ebec5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/themes/default/32px.png');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif') != 'e5ea073948ba83a6bc471d6ffddcec614b0bbe50') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif') !== 'e5ea073948ba83a6bc471d6ffddcec614b0bbe50') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif') !== '97925863eda2d3ca757736345b17562db7c9fb53') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif') !== 'e5ea073948ba83a6bc471d6ffddcec614b0bbe50') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/jstree/themes/default/throbber.gif');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js');
	writefile_21();
	if (!is_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js') != '36bbc98b10e364c10b61c4460b26b873dec2734a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js') !== '36bbc98b10e364c10b61c4460b26b873dec2734a') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js') !== '7413f3bc5f87d68b23efd82cef25da097535dfd7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_21();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js') !== '36bbc98b10e364c10b61c4460b26b873dec2734a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js');
	writefile_22();
	if (!is_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js') != '57b036ed502f1a84653ecd3bf96b669c284c2481') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js') !== '57b036ed502f1a84653ecd3bf96b669c284c2481') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js') !== 'a473367317e2a75960577610de164bd8f5c9ca73') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_22();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js') !== '57b036ed502f1a84653ecd3bf96b669c284c2481') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/jquery.layout_and_plugins.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/layout/layout-default.css')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/layout/layout-default.css');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('3p/layout/layout-default.css')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/layout/layout-default.css');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/layout/layout-default.css') != '697d0f5a77c2976a41665acafd76b2dcd4f4c15e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/layout-default.css');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/layout/layout-default.css', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/layout/layout-default.css');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/layout-default.css') !== '697d0f5a77c2976a41665acafd76b2dcd4f4c15e') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/layout-default.css') !== '496830f9f1ced4368cb1f7b388dc0672643b28a4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/layout/layout-default.css');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/layout/layout-default.css');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/layout/layout-default.css')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/layout/layout-default.css', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/layout-default.css') !== '697d0f5a77c2976a41665acafd76b2dcd4f4c15e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/layout-default.css');
		}
	}
}

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.buttons.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.buttons.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.buttons.js') !== '37d6efe4b0f5d2802dbbe928f1f0e8fcfc3f7563') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.buttons.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js');
	writefile_25();
	if (!is_file('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js') != '1b63699f6a410871d1680efc751d769635127ce4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js') !== '1b63699f6a410871d1680efc751d769635127ce4') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js') !== '6f4ccfb5dbbe287bf0001a5a8ec89dda51a5acfe') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_25();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js') !== '1b63699f6a410871d1680efc751d769635127ce4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/layout/plugins/jquery.layout.state.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	writefile_28();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') != '5f6defebc2cd95cf2b9af91ef813d1fc67e03dec') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== '5f6defebc2cd95cf2b9af91ef813d1fc67e03dec') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== 'd11715e707c2ce2ae5dc7a6419b9649f54485727') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_28();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== '5f6defebc2cd95cf2b9af91ef813d1fc67e03dec') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') != '33b89c29a7e82e7b72614484b20bd52e4e386fc1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '33b89c29a7e82e7b72614484b20bd52e4e386fc1') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '132d71e81c537343fa5d38d1ab31de195513bb5c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '33b89c29a7e82e7b72614484b20bd52e4e386fc1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
		}
	}
}

}

if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 417') err('Could not write to oidplus_version.txt!');
